caption.text:
Hack Club and @githubeducation have teamed up to give out prizes to teens this summer who build projects!

These are the steps to get started with Arcade!🕹️

- Go to hack.af/arcade
- Join the Hack Club Slack
- /hack in #arcade to log your hours! 

#hackclub #github #students #summer #circuits #coding #programming

caption.text:
Hack. Log. Share. Bank. 🕹️

This summer GitHub and Hack Club are partnering up to bring Arcade to teenagers across the world 🌎

how it works:
1. Join the Slack-set your summer project goals.
2. Hack on Projects-every hour you log is a ticket.
3. Get Cool Stuff-exchange your tickets for prizes.

Repeat all summer to earn Bambu 3D printers, Flipper Zeroes, breadboards, MacBooks, Logitech keyboards,
Framework laptops, soldering irons, boba ….. all the stuff you need to make more stuff

🔗hack.af/arcade

#coding #programming #students #teenagers #hackclub #github #arcade

caption.text:
☀️🕹️ This summer, GitHub and Hack Club are partnering up to create Arcade! Here’s how it works:
1. Join the Slack—set your summer project goals.
2. Hack on Projects—every hour you log is a ticket.
3. Get Cool Stuff—exchange your tickets for prizes.

Repeat all summer to earn Bambu 3D printers, Flipper Zeroes, breadboards, MacBooks, Logitech keyboards, Framework laptops, soldering irons, boba🧋… all the stuff you need to make more stuff.

🔗 hack.club/arcade-gh
